  <Title>Team Arena Release</Title>
  <Type>1</Type>
  <Content>On Wednesday, February 20th, Team Arena will be released. There are a few changes since beta.

-The team balancing has been slightly changed.

-The spawn area will be blocked off from the opposing team.

-Winning teams, in a match with 10 or more participants, will receive ability points and experience based on their current ability and insight.

-Winning matches (with 10 or more participants), will be recorded in the character's legend. Characters can purchase medals based on the number of wins.

Champion Medals - 5000 wins
Contender Medals - 2000 wins
Battler Medals - 500 wins
